---

<div style="text-align: center; padding: 3em 0 2em 0;">
  <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: 1.2;">Guiding Leaders From Success to Significance</h1>
  <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--text-color-secondary); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 2em auto; line-height: 1.6;">You've climbed the first mountain. Now there's a deeper journey calling.</p>
  <a href="/connect/" style="display: inline-block; padding: 1em 2.5em; background-color: var(--color-monarch-gold); color: var(--color-forest-floor); text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-family: var(--font-family-display); font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; transition: background-color 0.2s;">Request an Invitation</a>
</div>

<hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); margin: 3em 0;">

<h2>Where Are You on the Journey?</h2>

<div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 2em; margin: 3em 0;">
  <div style="padding: 1.5em; background-color: var(--background-secondary); border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.3rem;">The First Peak</h3>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">Success by all measures, yet something whispers: <em>Is this all there is?</em></p>
  </div>
  
  <div style="padding: 1.5em; background-color: var(--background-secondary); border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.3rem;">The Valley</h3>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">You've walked away from what no longer fits. The path ahead isn't clear yet. You're not lost, you're becoming.</p>
  </div>
  
  <div style="padding: 1.5em; background-color: var(--background-secondary); border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.3rem;">The Second Mountain</h3>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">A deeper climb ahead—one built on purpose, not just performance. You need guidance for this different ascent.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<p style="text-align: center; margin: 2em 0;"><a href="/journey/">Explore the two-mountain journey →</a></p>

<hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); margin: 3em 0;">

